6. Advanced Data Sync with Middleware
Objective: Learn to work with middleware platforms like MuleSoft or Zapier.

Challenge:

Set up a data sync between Salesforce and a database (e.g., MySQL) using a middleware tool.
Sync data bidirectionally: Salesforce Opportunities with database tables.
Bonus:

Implement error logging and retries for failed sync attempts.
Use middleware to transform data formats if needed.
